<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'roadmap' }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="page" id="main-content" role="main">
<section class="page-section">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:680px;">
    <div class="page-header a-fade-up">
      <div class="section-tag">roadmap</div>
      <h2>what we're building next</h2>
      <p>these are the features, improvements, and experiments we're working on — in approximate order. nothing here is guaranteed; everything here is what we believe in.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rm-list a-fade-up">
      <div class="rm-entry rm-shipped">
        <div class="rm-marker">&#10003;</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>email forward parsing</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge">shipped</span>
          </div>
          <p>forward renewal emails to your perch. inbox. we extract provider, amount, frequency, and renewal date automatically.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry rm-shipped">
        <div class="rm-marker">&#10003;</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>monday digest</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge">shipped</span>
          </div>
          <p>weekly roundup of everything renewing this week, with estimated costs and recommended actions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry rm-shipped">
        <div class="rm-marker">&#10003;</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>verdict engine</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge">shipped</span>
          </div>
          <p>for each renewal we determine: renew (it's competitive), renegotiate (you're overpaying), or cancel (it's not worth it).</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry">
        <div class="rm-marker rm-num">1</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>document upload</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge rm-badge-now">now</span>
          </div>
          <p>upload pdf invoices and policy documents directly. perch. extracts the same data as forwarded emails, for policies that arrive by post.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry">
        <div class="rm-marker rm-num">2</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>compare vs. market rates</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge rm-badge-next">next</span>
          </div>
          <p>benchmark your renewal price against anonymised market data for the same product, region, and profile. know if you're being overcharged relative to peers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry">
        <div class="rm-marker rm-num">3</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>smart calendar view</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge rm-badge-next">next</span>
          </div>
          <p>see all upcoming renewals on a timeline. filter by category, provider, or amount. sync with your existing calendar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry">
        <div class="rm-marker rm-num">4</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>one-click renegotiation prompts</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge rm-badge-next">next</span>
          </div>
          <p>when a renegotiate verdict fires, we show you what to say — draft scripts, comparison data, and a single click to open the right page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry">
        <div class="rm-marker rm-num">5</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>household sharing</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge rm-badge-later">later</span>
          </div>
          <p>share an inbox with your household. combined visibility into everyone's renewals — broadband, council tax, insurance, subscriptions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry">
        <div class="rm-marker rm-num">6</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>annual savings report</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge rm-badge-later">later</span>
          </div>
          <p>a year-end wrap-up showing every renewal, every verdict, and the total money saved by renegotiating or cancelling.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rm-entry">
        <div class="rm-marker rm-num">7</div>
        <div class="rm-body">
          <div class="rm-head">
            <h3>renewal price alerts</h3>
            <span class="rm-badge rm-badge-later">later</span>
          </div>
          <p>proactive push and email alerts when a renewal comes in above a threshold or above the previous period's price.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>